			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This dialogue takes place in two different states. The first is after the player has successfully fought back an army of goblins that attacked the druid grove. &#xD;&#xA;In the second state, the goblin leaders have been killed and the tieflings in the grove are leaving. She's aware of the hard work ahead required to make things go back to normal, but she's hopeful all the same.&#xD;&#xA;There's an extra node to acknowledge the missing idol, if it went missing before one of those two states were triggered." />
